\f0\b\fs28 \cf4 Layer 1 \'97 DOM Snapshot\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa120\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0\fs22 \cf0 Always available on any website. Captures the raw browser state of the selected element including computed styles \'97 what the browser actually resolved, not what was written in CSS.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li720\sa40\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f4\fs18 \cf5 dom: \{\
  html:       '<button disabled class="checkout-btn">Checkout</button>',\
