\f0\b\fs28 \cf4 Layer 4 \'97 Source Mapping\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa120\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0\fs22 \cf0 Available in dev mode builds on real localhost servers. React 18 stores source info inside _debugStack as an Error object with a full stack trace string. The file path and line number are parsed from this string.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li720\sa40\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

