\f0\b\fs36 \cf2 Design Principles\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs22 \cf0 1. Selection-first. 
\f2\b0 The element is the primary object, not the query.\

\f0\b 2. Layered \'97 not all-or-nothing. 
\f2\b0 Useful on any website. Each layer makes answers more precise.\

\f0\b 3. Structured data, not screenshots. 
\f2\b0 DOM nodes, computed styles, and component trees give Claude grounded reasoning.\

\f0\b 4. Claude as the reasoning layer. 
\f2\b0 The system captures and forwards. It does not interpret UI itself.\

\f0\b 5. Local-first. 
\f2\b0 Runs entirely on localhost. No cloud dependency for context capture.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

